The '''Technological University of the Mixteca''' ({{lang-es|Universidad Tecnológica de la Mixteca}}) ('''UTM'''), is a Mexican public university belonging to the SUNEO ({{lang-es|Sistema de Universidades Estatales de Oaxaca}}). UTM is located in [[Huajuapan de León]], [[Oaxaca]], region of [[the Mixteca]], [[Mexico]]. Its main areas of focus include: teaching, research, cultural diffusion and economic development.

